  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC398">
        <l>iṟappi ṉikaḻvi ṉetirvi ṉeṉṟac</l>
	<l>ciṟappuṭai marapi ṉammuk kālamun</l>
	<l>taṉmai muṉṉilai paṭarkkai yeṉṉu</l>
	<l>mammū viṭattāṉ viṉaiyiṉuṅ kuṟippiṉu</l>
	<l>meymmai yāṉu mīriraṇ ṭāku</l>
	<l>mavvā ṟeṉpa muṟṟiyaṉ moḻiyē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ivai viṉaiyiyaluḷ ōtappaṭṭaṉa cila coṟkaḷ, muṟṟuccol eṉṉum kuṟiyeytutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>ataṉāṟ payantatu eṉṉai yeṉiṉ, ac coṟku muṉpu muṭipukūṟi, īṇṭuk kuṟiyiṭṭāṉ eṉpatu payaṉ eṉpatu.</p>
<p>itaṉ poḻippu : iṟantakālam etirkālam nikaḻkālam eṉṉum mūṉṟukālamum uṭaiyavāyt, taṉmai muṉṉilai paṭarkkai yeṉṉum mūṉṟiṭattum viṉaiyum viṉaikkuṟippum paṟṟi, am mūṉṟiṭaṅkaṭōṟum viṉaiyum viṉaikkuṟippum eṉa iraṇṭām avvaṟukūṟṟuc coṟkaḷai muṟṟuccol eṉṟu kūṟupa āciriyar eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>'av vāṟu' eṉṟatu, taṉmai iraṇṭukuppaiyavāyum, muṉṉilai iraṇṭukuppaiyavāyum, paṭarkkai iraṇṭu kuppaiyavāyum varutal nōkki eṉpatu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu: 'uṇṭēṉ, kariyeṉ' eṉavum; 'uṇṭāy, kariyai' eṉavum; 'uṇṭāṉ, kariyaṉ' eṉavum varum. piṟavum aṉṉa.</p>
<p>'muṟṟuccol' eṉṟatu, ceykaiyum pālum kālamum ceyappaṭuporuḷum tōṉṟiniṟṟaliṉ muṟṟuc col eṉpārum, maṟṟōrcol nōkkātu muṭintu niṟṟaliṉ muṟṟuccol eṉpārum, ekkāl avai tam eccampeṟṟu niṉṟaṉa akkāl piṉ yātum nōkkāvāyc, ceppumūyiṟṟuppōla, amaintu māṟutaliṉ muṟṟuccol eṉpārum eṉa ippakutiyar āciriyar eṉpatu.	(31)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

